title: 30 for 30: Believeland
description:
The film shares with viewers some of the highs, lows and most unforgettable moments in Cleveland sports history over the past 50 years. Believeland includes interviews from celebrities, public figures and former athletes with connections to the city.

"This film is a testament to the unique power of sports to create communal bonds, regardless of the final score," Billman made in a statement. "Having cheered for Cleveland teams my whole life, I understand what it is like to be a fan whose love and loyalty have endured despite half a century of heartache and I hope that everyone who sees 'Believeland' will come away feeling some of that hard-earned love."
